        "subject": "LU-8674 obd: Add a general policy engine",
        "message": "LU-8674 obd: Add a general policy engine\n\nThis patch adds a general policy engine. And also HSM support\nis added for it.\n\nCurrently, only one archive ID is supported. And the archive ID\ncan be set by writing the ID to following proc:\n\n/proc/fs/lustre/mdt/*/hsm_policy_archive_id\n\nAnd an rule could be writting to following proc:\n\n/proc/fs/lustre/mdt/*/hsm_policy_rule\n\nThe rule should be in the form of Polish notation. A rule that will\ntrigger HSM archive action if the modify timestamp of the file is 1\nminute ealier than the system time looks like this:\n\n& - >= mtime - sys_time 60 1 hsma_bit_archive\n\nBy writing the FID to the following proc, the value of the rule on\nthe file could be printed by reading the proc of hsm_policy_rule.\n\n/proc/fs/lustre/mdt/*/hsm_policy_dump_obj\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I5b523e1bc7bf8372de5da5ab2a7cb72342d9608e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
